  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Smoking prevalence of adolescents in each group</measure>
    <time_frame>six years</time_frame>
    <description>We will compare the smoking prevalence of adolescents in each group at six years against the usual null hypothesis of no difference between groups. We will use the Chi-squared test, taking into account the &quot;variance inflation factor&quot; of the adolescent cluster and intraclass correlation coefficient.</description>
